&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div id="outline-container-org0c923ce" class="outline-3"&gt;
&lt;h3 id="org0c923ce"&gt;Proximate Layout&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org0c923ce"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
How well are related items placed near each other? Do the edges cross or do items overlap when perhaps they do not need to?
Are the crossings distracting?
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div id="outline-container-org9be58da" class="outline-3"&gt;
&lt;h3 id="org9be58da"&gt;Design of the Visulization&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org9be58da"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
Dose the visualization effectively use the assignment of variables to elements and design of a visualization?
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
